            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "sup"
              }
            ],
            "text": "210"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " the breeze fertiles it, a spring of crystal water sprays it."
          },
          {
            "type": "hard_break"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "My husband filled it with a multitude of noble flowers and said: “To you, Goddess, the sovereignty over flowers”."
          },
          {
            "type": "hard_break"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Often I wanted to classify and count their colors, without being able to manage it: there were too many to count."
          }
